  "title": "Accessibility (WCAG)",
  "html": "<h1 id=\"accessibility-wcag\"><a href=\"#accessibility-wcag\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Accessibility (WCAG)</h1></p><p>Making OSI Cards accessible to all users.</p><p><h2 id=\"built-in-features\"><a href=\"#built-in-features\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Built-in Features</h2></p><p><ul><li>Semantic HTML structure</li><li>ARIA labels on interactive elements</li><li>Keyboard navigation</li><li>Focus management</li><li>Color contrast compliance</li></ul>\n<h2 id=\"keyboard-navigation\"><a href=\"#keyboard-navigation\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Keyboard Navigation</h2></p><p><div class=\"table-wrapper\"><table><thead><tr><th>Key</th><th>Action</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Tab</td><td>Move between cards</td></tr><tr><td>Enter</td><td>Activate card/button</td></tr><tr><td>Escape</td><td>Close expanded card</td></tr><tr><td>Arrow keys</td><td>Navigate within card</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"screen-reader-support\"><a href=\"#screen-reader-support\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Screen Reader Support</h2></p><p>Cards use appropriate roles and labels:</p><p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\"><div class=\"code-header\"><span class=\"code-lang\">html</span><div class=\"code-actions\"><button class=\"copy-btn\" type=\"button\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div></div><pre><code class=\"language-html\">&amp;lt;article role=\"article\" aria-labelledby=\"card-title\"&amp;gt;<br>  &amp;lt;h2 id=\"card-title\"&amp;gt;Card Title&amp;lt;/h2&amp;gt;<br>  &amp;lt;section aria-label=\"Company Info\"&amp;gt;...&amp;lt;/section&amp;gt;<br>&amp;lt;/article&amp;gt;</code></pre></div></p><p><h2 id=\"high-contrast-mode\"><a href=\"#high-contrast-mode\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>High Contrast Mode</h2></p><p>Use high-contrast theme:</p><p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\"><div class=\"code-header\"><span class=\"code-lang\">typescript</span><div class=\"code-actions\"><button class=\"copy-btn\" type=\"button\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div></div><pre><code class=\"language-typescript\">themeService.setTheme('high-contrast');</code></pre></div></p><p><h2 id=\"testing\"><a href=\"#testing\" class=\"anchor-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Testing</h2></p><p><div class=\"code-block-wrapper\"><div class=\"code-header\"><span class=\"code-lang\">bash</span><div class=\"code-actions\"><button class=\"copy-btn\" type=\"button\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><rect x=\"9\" y=\"9\" width=\"13\" height=\"13\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M5 15H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V4a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div></div><pre><code class=\"language-bash\">npm run test:a11y<br>npm run wcag:audit</code></pre></div>\n",
